{"tid":766640,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[自信] 2&b：希望阿仙奴能為我驕傲","createTime":"2018-08-03T17:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T14:51:11.000Z","uid":135753,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"34cbdfc7497dae15b8afd15838548fcd6c43f596","tid":766640,"uid":135753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 2&amp;b：希望阿仙奴能為我驕傲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞前鋒伊禾比已經與阿仙奴續約，他希望能夠在球隊繼續進步。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞國腳表示：&ldquo;為阿仙奴效力是我兒時的夢想，能夠續約的感覺太好了，我希望能夠讓阿仙奴和家人為我感到驕傲。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我的第一件球衣就是阿仙奴的，我也希望能夠繼續披上槍手的戰袍。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我清楚我代表的是這支球隊，我需要傾盡全力。我不只代表我自己和我的家庭，我也代表著年輕一代。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴將在下週日開啟新賽季英超聯賽的征程，他們在聯賽首輪就會在主場面對衛冕冠軍曼城。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54b7609cf4d1d87d29345e7d6567e4b47459b0a","tid":766640,"uid":171157,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:54:06.000Z","msg":"無左條廢老<br />\n準備睇佢發光發亮"},{"pid":"a12460c4fa032a4f9a018e8aa358fdc70d3d731b","tid":766640,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"何來咁嘅自信.....？"},{"pid":"3bbdc562907d31fb0d5ae324c2461109141b6c03","tid":766640,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T19:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe42e99e1a54cc959652ea4c9837ed29fb43dbe","tid":766640,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T19:53:47.000Z","msg":"睇個topic就笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900b0aea1d5b70db